						class="[][ font-size:2 super-size-me ][]"
						style="line-height: 1"
					>Every feed is unique</span>
					<span
						class="[][ font-size:0 super-size-me ][]"
					>with the power of</span>
				</span>

				<span class="[][ font-regular font-size:2 ][ mute-em ]">Mute ‘Em</span>

				<span class="[][ font-regular font-size:1 ][]">technology</span>
			</p> #}

			{# <div
				class="[][ shadow ][ card card-feature ]"
			>
				<h2 class="[ stack ][ block-children font-regular font-size:0 super-size-me ][]">
					<span class="[][ bg-line ][]">
						<span class="[][][ bg-line-content font-condensed ]">Customize your feed with</span>
					</span>
					<span class="[][ bg-line ][]">
						<span class="[][][ bg-line-content font-condensed ]">Technology</span>
					</span>
				</h2>
			</div> #}
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
